I can't write anything that is my style right now so I tried to copy Deadmau5. Notes: 1. The drop is leGiT tRaSh :fire: :ok_hand: :weary: :b: I hope it sounded 2. I didn't mix it for bad speakers so you have to listen on headphones or good speakers 3. Chords are kinda generic
